                    <span>This is the single finest account of Hitler and the Third Reich, I believe that can be found. It's thorough, including biographies of important characters (Goebbels, Goering, Bormann etc.) It also gives a rarely seen,and fascinating intimate portrait of Hitler, and his machinations. Excellent for both beginners and starters on the Third Reich.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Still Popular</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
